body:
See flutter-idea/README.md for a description of the goal of the PR.

It will be easier to make sense of the top-level build.gradle if it is reviewed without comparing to the old one. The old one had some integration test support that is no longer relevant, so it was only useful for running unit tests. I tried to remove all non-essential declarations.

Mods to the plugin tool are coming later (if this doesn't cause CI to go red).
title: Build with Gradle
